    "body": [
        {
            "value": "<p>In addition to recording tuba on albums as a leader and sideman, Ray Draper appeared as a vocalist on the soundtrack to the film <a href=\"https:\/\/en.wikipedia.org\/wiki\/Last_Summer\"><em>Last Summer<\/em><\/a> and had his compositions recorded by contemporaries, including:<\/p><ul><li><em>The Biddie Griddies<\/em>,&nbsp;<em>Ugh!<\/em>, and&nbsp;<em>Reflections of Buhaina<\/em> on&nbsp;<a href=\"https:\/\/en.wikipedia.org\/wiki\/A_Midnight_Session_with_the_Jazz_Messengers\"><em>A Midnight Session with the Jazz Messengers<\/em><\/a><\/li><li><em>Jackie's Ghost<\/em> on <a href=\"https:\/\/en.wikipedia.org\/wiki\/Makin%27_the_Changes\"><em>Makin' the Changes<\/em><\/a><\/li><\/ul>",
